This is a small program in OpenGL using the API glut.
The project represent the indianapolis motor way.

For a quick overview please go to : 
<http://matth.daniel.free.fr/openGL/indianapolis>

1 - Requirements 
	- freeglut3-dev
	- libjpeg8-dev
	- libtiff4-dev

The program was compiled on : 
	- Mac osX 10.6
	- Ubuntu 12.04 LTS

2 - Documentation
Not available at the moment!

